SubShader {

#define HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS 1

#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)

#endif
uniform 	vec4 _Time;
uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[20];
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerDraw {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];

UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(_DigiDistore);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RampMap_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;

in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;

void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_30, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);

    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * _Emissive;

    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;

        u_xlat28 = float(int(u_xlatu_loop_1));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb15 = !!(u_xlat28<2.0);

        u_xlat29 = u_xlat28 + -2.0;
        u_xlat28 = (u_xlatb15) ? u_xlat28 : u_xlat29;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb28 = !!(u_xlat28<1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb28 = u_xlat28<1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_30 = (u_xlatb28) ? u_xlat16_10.x : u_xlat16_10.y;
        u_xlati28 = int(u_xlat16_30);
        u_xlat15.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPosition[u_xlati28].xyz;
        u_xlat5.x = dot(u_xlat15.xyz, u_xlat15.xyz);
        u_xlat5.x = max(u_xlat5.x, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat19 = inversesqrt(u_xlat5.x);
        u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat15.xyz * vec3(u_xlat19);
        u_xlat19 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat5.x);
        u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati28].x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati28].y;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat5.x = min(max(u_xlat5.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat5.x = clamp(u_xlat5.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat19;
        u_xlat16_30 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDir[u_xlati28].xyz, u_xlat15.xyz);
        u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati28].z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati28].w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_30 = min(max(u_xlat16_30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_30 = clamp(u_xlat16_30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 * u_xlat16_30;
        u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_30 * u_xlat5.x;
        u_xlat16_30 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat15.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_30 = min(max(u_xlat16_30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_30 = clamp(u_xlat16_30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_30) * _AdditionalLightsColor[u_xlati28].xyz;
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat5.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
        u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat11.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xx * u_xlat11.xy;
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_RampMap, u_xlat16_2.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb42 = !!(_DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978);
#else
    u_xlatb42 = _DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978;
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (u_xlatb42) ? -1.0 : u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat42 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = vec2(u_xlat42) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat16_42 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat1.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_16 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_16 = min(u_xlat16_16, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_16 * u_xlat16_2.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat16_42 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat42 = (-u_xlat16_2.x) + u_xlat42;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat42 = min(max(u_xlat42, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat42 = clamp(u_xlat42, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-_DigiBaseColor0.xyz) * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat42) * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat15.xyz;
    u_xlat42 = vs_TEXCOORD2.x + (-_ClipValueCloth);
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / _ClipWidthCloth;
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat42 * u_xlat1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat42 = min(max(u_xlat42, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat42 = clamp(u_xlat42, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat42 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat42 * u_xlat42;
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat42 * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = _ClipColor.xyz + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat42) * u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"

    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;

    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat10_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat10_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat10_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_30, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat10_1.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;

    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat42) * u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(_DigiDistore);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _FurTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(8) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampMap;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
vec4 u_xlat7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_10;
vec4 u_xlat11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
vec4 u_xlat16;
vec3 u_xlat17;
vec3 u_xlat19;
mediump float u_xlat16_20;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_22;
vec2 u_xlat23;
float u_xlat27;
float u_xlat34;
uint u_xlatu34;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
float u_xlat51;
mediump float u_xlat16_51;
int u_xlati51;
bool u_xlatb51;
float u_xlat53;
bool u_xlatb53;
mediump float u_xlat16_54;
mediump float u_xlat16_55;
mediump float u_xlat16_56;
float u_xlat57;
float u_xlat58;
float u_xlat59;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_0.x * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * _FurShape;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_0.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat17.xz = u_xlat16_1.xx * vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MainTex, u_xlat17.xz);
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_3.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_2.z));
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_3.x = exp2(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_20 = u_xlat16_2.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_2.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_3.z = max(u_xlat16_37, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_3.xz = min(u_xlat16_3.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_54 = u_xlat16_2.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_54 = u_xlat16_54 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat16_4.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyw;

    u_xlat16_22.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat16_22.xyz + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = max(u_xlat16_22.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = min(u_xlat16_22.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * vec3(0.318309873, 0.318309873, 0.318309873) + u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    for(uint u_xlatu_loop_1 = uint(0u) ; u_xlatu_loop_1<u_xlatu0 ; u_xlatu_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat51 = float(int(u_xlatu_loop_1));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb53 = !!(u_xlat51<2.0);
#else
        u_xlatb53 = u_xlat51<2.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_12.xy = (bool(u_xlatb53)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat6.x = u_xlat51 + -2.0;
        u_xlat51 = (u_xlatb53) ? u_xlat51 : u_xlat6.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb51 = !!(u_xlat51<1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb51 = u_xlat51<1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_37 = (u_xlatb51) ? u_xlat16_12.x : u_xlat16_12.y;
        u_xlati51 = int(u_xlat16_37);
        u_xlat6.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPosition[u_xlati51].xyz;
        u_xlat53 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
        u_xlat53 = max(u_xlat53, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat57 = inversesqrt(u_xlat53);
        u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat57) * u_xlat6.xyz;
        u_xlat57 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat53);
        u_xlat53 = u_xlat53 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati51].x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati51].y;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat53 = min(max(u_xlat53, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat53 = clamp(u_xlat53, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat53 = u_xlat53 * u_xlat57;
        u_xlat16_37 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDir[u_xlati51].xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
        u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_37 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati51].z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati51].w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_37 = min(max(u_xlat16_37, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_37 = clamp(u_xlat16_37, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_37 * u_xlat16_37;
        u_xlat53 = u_xlat53 * u_xlat16_37;
        u_xlat16_37 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_37 = min(max(u_xlat16_37, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_37 = clamp(u_xlat16_37, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * _AdditionalLightsColor[u_xlati51].xyz;
        u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat53) * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
        u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat0.xzw = (-u_xlat2.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat2.zxy) + (-u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat53 = dot(u_xlat0.xzw, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat53 = inversesqrt(u_xlat53);
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat0.xzw * vec3(u_xlat53);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat0.zwx * (-u_xlat2.zxy);
    u_xlat6.xyz = (-u_xlat2.yzx) * u_xlat0.wxz + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat53 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat53 = inversesqrt(u_xlat53);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat53) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat7.x = dot(u_xlat0.xzw, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat7.y = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat7.z = dot((-u_xlat2.xyz), u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat7.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xx * u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_0.xzw = texture(_RampMap, u_xlat16_3.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.www * u_xlat16_0.xzw;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat17.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb51 = !!(_DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978);
#else
    u_xlatb51 = _DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978;
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (u_xlatb51) ? -1.0 : u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat51 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat2.xy = vec2(u_xlat51) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat2.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat2.xy;
    u_xlat16_51 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat2.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_20 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_20 = min(u_xlat16_20, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_20 * u_xlat16_3.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat51 = u_xlat16_51 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat51 = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + u_xlat51;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat51 = min(max(u_xlat51, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat51 = clamp(u_xlat51, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat2.x = log2(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat2.x = exp2(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat2.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat19.xyz = u_xlat2.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-_DigiBaseColor0.xyz) * u_xlat2.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat51) * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat19.xyz;
    u_xlat51 = vs_TEXCOORD2.x + (-_ClipValueCloth);
    u_xlat2.x = float(1.0) / _ClipWidthCloth;
    u_xlat51 = u_xlat51 * u_xlat2.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat51 = min(max(u_xlat51, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat51 = clamp(u_xlat51, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat51 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat51 = u_xlat51 * u_xlat51;
    u_xlat51 = u_xlat51 * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat2.xyz = _ClipColor.xyz + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat51) * u_xlat2.xyz + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_20 * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_1.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_14.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = max(u_xlat16_13.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = min(u_xlat16_13.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = vec3(u_xlat16_54) * u_xlat10_1.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_55 = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlati0 = int(u_xlat16_55);
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat57 * u_xlat51 + (-u_xlat57);
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat57 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_55 = u_xlat34 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat16_55 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat16_55;
    u_xlat16_55 = u_xlat51 / u_xlat16_55;
    u_xlat16_37 = (-u_xlat16_3.z) * u_xlat16_3.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_37 + u_xlat16_56;
    u_xlat51 = u_xlat17.x * u_xlat16_37 + u_xlat16_56;
    u_xlat51 = u_xlat51 * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat17.x * u_xlat34 + u_xlat51;
    u_xlat34 = 0.5 / u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat51 = (-u_xlat58) + 1.0;
    u_xlat53 = u_xlat51 * u_xlat51;
    u_xlat53 = u_xlat53 * u_xlat53;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat51 * u_xlat53;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat7.y * 50.0;
    u_xlat16_37 = clamp(u_xlat16_37, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_22.x = (-u_xlat51) * u_xlat53 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * u_xlat16_22.xxx;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat6.xxx + u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat16_55;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat16_22.xyz + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = max(u_xlat16_22.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = min(u_xlat16_22.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * vec3(0.318309873, 0.318309873, 0.318309873) + u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    for(int u_xlati_loop_1 = 0 ; u_xlati_loop_1<u_xlati0 ; u_xlati_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat51 = float(u_xlati_loop_1);
        u_xlatb53 = u_xlat51<2.0;
        u_xlat16_12.xy = (bool(u_xlatb53)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat6.x = u_xlat51 + -2.0;
        u_xlat51 = (u_xlatb53) ? u_xlat51 : u_xlat6.x;
        u_xlatb51 = u_xlat51<1.0;
        u_xlat16_37 = (u_xlatb51) ? u_xlat16_12.x : u_xlat16_12.y;
        u_xlati51 = int(u_xlat16_37);
        u_xlat6.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPositionDynamicIndex(u_xlati51).xyz;
        u_xlat53 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
        u_xlat53 = max(u_xlat53, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat57 = inversesqrt(u_xlat53);
        u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat57) * u_xlat6.xyz;
        u_xlat57 = float(1.0) / u_xlat53;
        u_xlat53 = u_xlat53 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati51).x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati51).y;
        u_xlat53 = clamp(u_xlat53, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat53 = u_xlat53 * u_xlat57;
        u_xlat16_37 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDirDynamicIndex(u_xlati51).xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
        u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_37 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati51).z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati51).w;
        u_xlat16_37 = clamp(u_xlat16_37, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_37 * u_xlat16_37;
        u_xlat53 = u_xlat53 * u_xlat16_37;
        u_xlat16_37 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
        u_xlat16_37 = clamp(u_xlat16_37, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * _AdditionalLightsColorDynamicIndex(u_xlati51).xyz;
        u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat53) * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
        u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat0.xzw = (-u_xlat2.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat2.zxy) + (-u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat53 = dot(u_xlat0.xzw, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat53 = inversesqrt(u_xlat53);
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat0.xzw * vec3(u_xlat53);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat0.zwx * (-u_xlat2.zxy);
    u_xlat6.xyz = (-u_xlat2.yzx) * u_xlat0.wxz + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat53 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat53 = inversesqrt(u_xlat53);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat53) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat7.x = dot(u_xlat0.xzw, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat7.y = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat7.z = dot((-u_xlat2.xyz), u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat7.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xx * u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10_0.xzw = texture2D(_RampMap, u_xlat16_3.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_1.www * u_xlat10_0.xzw;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat17.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlatb51 = _DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978;
    u_xlat16_3.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (u_xlatb51) ? -1.0 : u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat51 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat2.xy = vec2(u_xlat51) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat2.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat2.xy;
    u_xlat10_51 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat2.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_20 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_20 = min(u_xlat16_20, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_20 * u_xlat16_3.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat51 = u_xlat10_51 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat51 = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + u_xlat51;
    u_xlat51 = clamp(u_xlat51, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.x = log2(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat2.x = exp2(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat2.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat19.xyz = u_xlat2.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-_DigiBaseColor0.xyz) * u_xlat2.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat51) * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat19.xyz;
    u_xlat51 = vs_TEXCOORD2.x + (-_ClipValueCloth);
    u_xlat2.x = float(1.0) / _ClipWidthCloth;
    u_xlat51 = u_xlat51 * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat51 = clamp(u_xlat51, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat51 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat51 = u_xlat51 * u_xlat51;
    u_xlat51 = u_xlat51 * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat2.xyz = _ClipColor.xyz + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat51) * u_xlat2.xyz + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(_DigiDistore);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampMap;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
bool u_xlatb5;
vec4 u_xlat6;
bool u_xlatb6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
float u_xlat13;
uint u_xlatu13;
vec3 u_xlat14;
mediump float u_xlat16_15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_17;
float u_xlat18;
vec3 u_xlat20;
float u_xlat26;
int u_xlati26;
bool u_xlatb26;
mediump float u_xlat16_28;
mediump float u_xlat16_30;
float u_xlat33;
float u_xlat39;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
bool u_xlatb39;
mediump float u_xlat16_41;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
mediump float u_xlat16_43;
float u_xlat44;
bool u_xlatb44;
float u_xlat45;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat6.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat6, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_43 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_43;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb44 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb44 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb6 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb6 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb44 = u_xlatb44 || u_xlatb6;
    u_xlat16_42 = (u_xlatb44) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_43 = (-u_xlat16_15) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_43 = (-u_xlat16_43) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_15;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15 = min(max(u_xlat16_15, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15 = clamp(u_xlat16_15, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_15) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_15) * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_15 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) + u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_15 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15 = min(max(u_xlat16_15, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15 = clamp(u_xlat16_15, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat44 = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat7.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat14.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = abs(u_xlat16_4.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat45 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat45 = min(max(u_xlat45, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat45 = clamp(u_xlat45, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat7.x = dot(u_xlat14.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat7.x = min(max(u_xlat7.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat7.x = clamp(u_xlat7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_3.y;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat16_3.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat20.z = u_xlat20.x * 0.125 + u_xlat33;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat20.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat33);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat20.zx + vec2(0.125, 0.125);
    u_xlat16_17.xy = max(u_xlat9.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_17.xy = u_xlat16_17.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_17.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.x = dot((-u_xlat14.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x + u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-u_xlat16_17.xxx) + (-u_xlat14.xyz);
    u_xlat20.x = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat20.x * u_xlat20.x;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_30;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_9 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_9.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_30 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_30 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_30 = max(u_xlat16_30, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_30 = log2(u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_30 = exp2(u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat16_43 + 1.0;
    u_xlat20.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat20.x;
    u_xlat20.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat20.xxx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat6.xyz) + vec3(u_xlat16_15);
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xxx * u_xlat9.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat20.xyz = u_xlat20.xyz * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat20.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat20.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat5.x = (-u_xlat45) * u_xlat45 + 1.0;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat45;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat18 * u_xlat18 + u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_43 / u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat16_2.z * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat18;
    u_xlat5.x = min(u_xlat5.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_42 + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15 = min(max(u_xlat16_15, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15 = clamp(u_xlat16_15, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat20.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_15) + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_15) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15 = min(max(u_xlat16_15, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15 = clamp(u_xlat16_15, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_15) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = max(u_xlat16_11.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = min(u_xlat16_11.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15 = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_2.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat5.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-u_xlat5.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_15 * u_xlat16_17.x + u_xlat18;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_15 / u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_17.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_17.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_17.x);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_17.x = min(max(u_xlat16_17.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_17.x = clamp(u_xlat16_17.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_15 * u_xlat16_2.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_15 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_15 * u_xlat16_2.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_2.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_15;
    u_xlat16_15 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat16_15 + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_15 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = max(u_xlat16_11.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = min(u_xlat16_11.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyw = vec3(u_xlat16_41) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_42 = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlatu0 = uint(int(u_xlat16_42));
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat44 + (-u_xlat45);
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat45 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat13 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat44 / u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_28 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) * u_xlat16_2.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_28 + u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat16_28 + u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat26 * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat13 + u_xlat26;
    u_xlat16_28 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat16_28);
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat16_28 * 0.5;
    u_xlat26 = (-u_xlat7.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat26 * u_xlat26;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat26 * u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat6.y * 50.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_28 = min(max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-u_xlat26) * u_xlat5.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * u_xlat16_17.xxx;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * vec3(u_xlat18) + u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * u_xlat16_17.xyz + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = max(u_xlat16_17.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = min(u_xlat16_17.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * vec3(0.318309873, 0.318309873, 0.318309873) + u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyw;
    for(uint u_xlatu_loop_1 = uint(0u) ; u_xlatu_loop_1<u_xlatu0 ; u_xlatu_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat26 = float(int(u_xlatu_loop_1));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb5 = !!(u_xlat26<2.0);
#else
        u_xlatb5 = u_xlat26<2.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_10.xy = (bool(u_xlatb5)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat18 = u_xlat26 + -2.0;
        u_xlat26 = (u_xlatb5) ? u_xlat26 : u_xlat18;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb26 = !!(u_xlat26<1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb26 = u_xlat26<1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_28 = (u_xlatb26) ? u_xlat16_10.x : u_xlat16_10.y;
        u_xlati26 = int(u_xlat16_28);
        u_xlat5.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPosition[u_xlati26].xyz;
        u_xlat44 = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
        u_xlat44 = max(u_xlat44, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat6.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat44);
        u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat6.xxx;
        u_xlat6.x = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat44);
        u_xlat44 = u_xlat44 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati26].x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati26].y;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat44 = min(max(u_xlat44, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat44 = clamp(u_xlat44, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat44 = u_xlat44 * u_xlat6.x;
        u_xlat16_28 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDir[u_xlati26].xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
        u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati26].z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati26].w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_28 = min(max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28 * u_xlat16_28;
        u_xlat44 = u_xlat16_28 * u_xlat44;
        u_xlat16_28 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_28 = min(max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * _AdditionalLightsColor[u_xlati26].xyz;
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat44) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
        u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-u_xlat14.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat14.zxy) + (-u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat5.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat5.x);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat5.xxx;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * (-u_xlat14.zxy);
    u_xlat5.xyz = (-u_xlat14.yzx) * u_xlat0.zxy + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat44 = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat44 = inversesqrt(u_xlat44);
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat44) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot((-u_xlat14.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat0.xy * u_xlat16_2.xx;
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_RampMap, u_xlat16_2.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb39 = !!(_DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978);
#else
    u_xlatb39 = _DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978;
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (u_xlatb39) ? -1.0 : u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat39 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = vec2(u_xlat39) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat16_39 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat1.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_15 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_15 = min(u_xlat16_15, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_15 * u_xlat16_2.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat16_39 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat39 = (-u_xlat16_2.x) + u_xlat39;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat39 = min(max(u_xlat39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat39 = clamp(u_xlat39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-_DigiBaseColor0.xyz) * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat39) * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat14.xyz;
    u_xlat39 = vs_TEXCOORD2.x + (-_ClipValueCloth);
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / _ClipWidthCloth;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 * u_xlat1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat39 = min(max(u_xlat39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat39 = clamp(u_xlat39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat39 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = _ClipColor.xyz + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat39) * u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

{

    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;

    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;

    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;

    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;

    u_xlat16_17.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * vec3(u_xlat18) + u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * u_xlat16_17.xyz + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = max(u_xlat16_17.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = min(u_xlat16_17.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * vec3(0.318309873, 0.318309873, 0.318309873) + u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyw;
    for(int u_xlati_loop_1 = 0 ; u_xlati_loop_1<u_xlati0 ; u_xlati_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat26 = float(u_xlati_loop_1);
        u_xlatb5 = u_xlat26<2.0;
        u_xlat16_10.xy = (bool(u_xlatb5)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat18 = u_xlat26 + -2.0;
        u_xlat26 = (u_xlatb5) ? u_xlat26 : u_xlat18;
        u_xlatb26 = u_xlat26<1.0;
        u_xlat16_28 = (u_xlatb26) ? u_xlat16_10.x : u_xlat16_10.y;
        u_xlati26 = int(u_xlat16_28);
        u_xlat5.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPositionDynamicIndex(u_xlati26).xyz;
        u_xlat44 = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
        u_xlat44 = max(u_xlat44, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat6.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat44);
        u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat6.xxx;
        u_xlat6.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat44;
        u_xlat44 = u_xlat44 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati26).x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati26).y;
        u_xlat44 = clamp(u_xlat44, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat44 = u_xlat44 * u_xlat6.x;
        u_xlat16_28 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDirDynamicIndex(u_xlati26).xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
        u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati26).z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati26).w;
        u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28 * u_xlat16_28;
        u_xlat44 = u_xlat16_28 * u_xlat44;
        u_xlat16_28 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
        u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * _AdditionalLightsColorDynamicIndex(u_xlati26).xyz;
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat44) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
        u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-u_xlat14.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat14.zxy) + (-u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat5.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat5.x);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat5.xxx;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * (-u_xlat14.zxy);
    u_xlat5.xyz = (-u_xlat14.yzx) * u_xlat0.zxy + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat44 = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat44 = inversesqrt(u_xlat44);
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat44) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot((-u_xlat14.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat0.xy * u_xlat16_2.xx;
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_RampMap, u_xlat16_2.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat10_0.www * u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlatb39 = _DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978;
    u_xlat16_2.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (u_xlatb39) ? -1.0 : u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat39 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = vec2(u_xlat39) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat10_39 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat1.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_15 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_15 = min(u_xlat16_15, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_15 * u_xlat16_2.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat10_39 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat39 = (-u_xlat16_2.x) + u_xlat39;
    u_xlat39 = clamp(u_xlat39, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-_DigiBaseColor0.xyz) * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat39) * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat14.xyz;
    u_xlat39 = vs_TEXCOORD2.x + (-_ClipValueCloth);
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / _ClipWidthCloth;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat39 = clamp(u_xlat39, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat39 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = _ClipColor.xyz + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat39) * u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

"
}

UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(_DigiDistore);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;

UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampMap;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;

void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_30, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_45 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_45 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_45);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_45) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat6.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_45 = dot(u_xlat6, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_46 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat16_45 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_46;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb47 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb47 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb6 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb6 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb47 = u_xlatb47 || u_xlatb6;
    u_xlat16_45 = (u_xlatb47) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_46 = (-u_xlat16_16) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_46 = (-u_xlat16_46) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_16;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_16 = min(max(u_xlat16_16, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_16 = clamp(u_xlat16_16, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_16) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_16) * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_16 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) + u_xlat16_46;
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_16 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_16 = min(max(u_xlat16_16, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_16 = clamp(u_xlat16_16, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_46 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat47 = u_xlat16_46 * u_xlat16_46;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat7.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat15.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = abs(u_xlat16_4.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat48 = min(max(u_xlat48, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat48 = clamp(u_xlat48, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat7.x = dot(u_xlat15.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat7.x = min(max(u_xlat7.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat7.x = clamp(u_xlat7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_3.y;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat16_3.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat21.z = u_xlat21.x * 0.125 + u_xlat35;
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat21.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat35);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat21.zx + vec2(0.125, 0.125);
    u_xlat16_18.xy = max(u_xlat9.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_18.xy = u_xlat16_18.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_18.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat21.x = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat21.x * u_xlat21.x;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat21.xyz = (-u_xlat15.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat21.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat15.zxy) + (-u_xlat21.xyz);
    u_xlat9.x = dot(u_xlat21.xyz, u_xlat21.xyz);
    u_xlat9.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat9.x);
    u_xlat21.xyz = u_xlat21.xyz * u_xlat9.xxx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat15.zxy) * u_xlat21.yzx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat15.yzx) * u_xlat21.zxy + (-u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat51 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat51 = inversesqrt(u_xlat51);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat51) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat11.x = dot(u_xlat21.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat11.y = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat11.z = dot((-u_xlat15.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat15.x = dot(u_xlat11.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat15.x);
    u_xlat15.xy = u_xlat15.xx * u_xlat11.xy;
    u_xlat15.xy = u_xlat15.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_32 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_32 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_32;
    u_xlat16_32 = u_xlat16_32 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = textureLod(_MatMap, u_xlat15.xy, u_xlat16_32).xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * vec3(_MatMapMul);
    u_xlat15.x = u_xlat16_46 * u_xlat16_46 + 1.0;
    u_xlat15.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat15.x;
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat15.xxx;
    u_xlat21.xyz = (-u_xlat6.xyz) + vec3(u_xlat16_16);
    u_xlat21.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xxx * u_xlat21.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat15.xyz * u_xlat21.xyz;
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_45) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat5.x = (-u_xlat48) * u_xlat48 + 1.0;
    u_xlat19 = u_xlat16_46 * u_xlat48;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat19 * u_xlat19 + u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_46 / u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat19 = u_xlat16_2.z * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat19;
    u_xlat5.x = min(u_xlat5.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_45 + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_16 = min(max(u_xlat16_16, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_16 = clamp(u_xlat16_16, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat15.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_16) + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_16 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_16);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_16) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_12.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_16 = min(max(u_xlat16_16, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_16 = clamp(u_xlat16_16, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_16) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = max(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = min(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16 = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat15.x = u_xlat16_2.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat15.x = u_xlat15.x * u_xlat15.x;
    u_xlat29 = u_xlat15.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-u_xlat15.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_16 * u_xlat16_18.x + u_xlat29;
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_16 / u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_18.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_18.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_18.x);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.x = dot(u_xlat16_12.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_18.x = min(max(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_18.x = clamp(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_16 * u_xlat16_2.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_16 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_16 * u_xlat16_2.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_2.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_16;
    u_xlat16_16 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_16 = u_xlat16_45 * u_xlat16_16 + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_16 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_13.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = max(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = min(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyw = vec3(u_xlat16_44) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_45 = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlatu0 = uint(int(u_xlat16_45));
    u_xlat14 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat47 + (-u_xlat48);
    u_xlat14 = u_xlat14 * u_xlat48 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat14 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat14 * u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat47 / u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) * u_xlat16_2.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat14 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_30 + u_xlat16_46;
    u_xlat28 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat16_30 + u_xlat16_46;
    u_xlat28 = u_xlat28 * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat14 + u_xlat28;
    u_xlat16_30 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat14 = u_xlat16_30 * 0.5;
    u_xlat28 = (-u_xlat7.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat15.x = u_xlat28 * u_xlat28;
    u_xlat15.x = u_xlat15.x * u_xlat15.x;
    u_xlat29 = u_xlat28 * u_xlat15.x;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat6.y * 50.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_30 = min(max(u_xlat16_30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_30 = clamp(u_xlat16_30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-u_xlat28) * u_xlat15.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * u_xlat16_18.xxx;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_30) * vec3(u_xlat29) + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat14 * u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_30) * u_xlat16_18.xyz + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = max(u_xlat16_18.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = min(u_xlat16_18.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * vec3(0.318309873, 0.318309873, 0.318309873) + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyw;
    for(uint u_xlatu_loop_1 = uint(0u) ; u_xlatu_loop_1<u_xlatu0 ; u_xlatu_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat28 = float(int(u_xlatu_loop_1));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb15 = !!(u_xlat28<2.0);
#else
        u_xlatb15 = u_xlat28<2.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_10.xy = (bool(u_xlatb15)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat29 = u_xlat28 + -2.0;
        u_xlat28 = (u_xlatb15) ? u_xlat28 : u_xlat29;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb28 = !!(u_xlat28<1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb28 = u_xlat28<1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_30 = (u_xlatb28) ? u_xlat16_10.x : u_xlat16_10.y;

        u_xlat15.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPosition[u_xlati28].xyz;

        u_xlat5.x = max(u_xlat5.x, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat19 = inversesqrt(u_xlat5.x);
        u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat15.xyz * vec3(u_xlat19);
        u_xlat19 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat5.x);
        u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati28].x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati28].y;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat5.x = min(max(u_xlat5.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat5.x = clamp(u_xlat5.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat19;
        u_xlat16_30 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDir[u_xlati28].xyz, u_xlat15.xyz);
        u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati28].z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati28].w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_30 = min(max(u_xlat16_30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_30 = clamp(u_xlat16_30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 * u_xlat16_30;
        u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_30 * u_xlat5.x;
        u_xlat16_30 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat15.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_30 = min(max(u_xlat16_30, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_30 = clamp(u_xlat16_30, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_30) * _AdditionalLightsColor[u_xlati28].xyz;
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat5.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
        u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat11.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);

    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);

    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat16_8.xyz;

    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);

    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));

    u_xlatb42 = !!(_DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978);
#else

#endif
    u_xlat16_2.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;

    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);

        u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati28).z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati28).w;
        u_xlat16_30 = clamp(u_xlat16_30, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 * u_xlat16_30;
        u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_30 * u_xlat5.x;
        u_xlat16_30 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat15.xyz);
        u_xlat16_30 = clamp(u_xlat16_30, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_30) * _AdditionalLightsColorDynamicIndex(u_xlati28).xyz;
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat5.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
        u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat11.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xx * u_xlat11.xy;
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_RampMap, u_xlat16_2.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat10_0.www * u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz / u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlatb42 = _DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978;
    u_xlat16_2.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (u_xlatb42) ? -1.0 : u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat42 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = vec2(u_xlat42) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat10_42 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat1.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_16 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_16 = min(u_xlat16_16, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_16 * u_xlat16_2.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat10_42 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat42 = (-u_xlat16_2.x) + u_xlat42;
    u_xlat42 = clamp(u_xlat42, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-_DigiBaseColor0.xyz) * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat42) * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat15.xyz;
    u_xlat42 = vs_TEXCOORD2.x + (-_ClipValueCloth);
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / _ClipWidthCloth;
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat42 * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat42 = clamp(u_xlat42, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat42 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat42 * u_xlat42;
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat42 * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = _ClipColor.xyz + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat42) * u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}
