    u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_52 = (-u_xlat48) * u_xlat50 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_52);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat6.xxx + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat32 * u_xlat16_21.x;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_12.xyz + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = max(u_xlat16_21.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = min(u_xlat16_21.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * vec3(0.318309873, 0.318309873, 0.318309873) + u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    for(int u_xlati_loop_1 = 0 ; u_xlati_loop_1<u_xlati0 ; u_xlati_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat48 = float(u_xlati_loop_1);
        u_xlatb50 = u_xlat48<2.0;
        u_xlat16_12.xy = (bool(u_xlatb50)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat6.x = u_xlat48 + -2.0;
        u_xlat48 = (u_xlatb50) ? u_xlat48 : u_xlat6.x;
        u_xlatb48 = u_xlat48<1.0;
        u_xlat16_35 = (u_xlatb48) ? u_xlat16_12.x : u_xlat16_12.y;
        u_xlati48 = int(u_xlat16_35);
        u_xlat6.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPositionDynamicIndex(u_xlati48).xyz;
        u_xlat50 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
        u_xlat50 = max(u_xlat50, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat54 = inversesqrt(u_xlat50);
        u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat54) * u_xlat6.xyz;
        u_xlat54 = float(1.0) / u_xlat50;
        u_xlat50 = u_xlat50 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati48).x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati48).y;
        u_xlat50 = clamp(u_xlat50, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat50 = u_xlat50 * u_xlat54;
        u_xlat16_35 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDirDynamicIndex(u_xlati48).xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
        u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati48).z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati48).w;
        u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35;
        u_xlat50 = u_xlat50 * u_xlat16_35;
        u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
        u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * _AdditionalLightsColorDynamicIndex(u_xlati48).xyz;
        u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat50) * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat0.xzw = (-u_xlat2.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat0.xzw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat2.zxy) + (-u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat50 = dot(u_xlat0.xzw, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat50 = inversesqrt(u_xlat50);
    u_xlat0.xzw = u_xlat0.xzw * vec3(u_xlat50);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat0.zwx * (-u_xlat2.zxy);
    u_xlat6.xyz = (-u_xlat2.yzx) * u_xlat0.wxz + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat50 = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat50 = inversesqrt(u_xlat50);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat50) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat8.x = dot(u_xlat0.xzw, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat8.y = dot(u_xlat6.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat8.z = dot((-u_xlat2.xyz), u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_3.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xx * u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat10_0.xzw = texture2D(_RampMap, u_xlat16_3.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_1.www * u_xlat10_0.xzw;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz / u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlatb48 = _DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978;
    u_xlat16_3.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (u_xlatb48) ? -1.0 : u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat48 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat2.xy = vec2(u_xlat48) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat2.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat2.xy;
    u_xlat10_48 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat2.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_19 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_19 = min(u_xlat16_19, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_19 * u_xlat16_3.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat10_48 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat48 = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + u_xlat48;
    u_xlat48 = clamp(u_xlat48, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.x = log2(u_xlat16_5.x);
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat2.x = exp2(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat2.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat18.xyz = u_xlat2.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-_DigiBaseColor0.xyz) * u_xlat2.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat48) * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat18.xyz;
    u_xlat48 = vs_TEXCOORD2.x + (-_ClipValueCloth);
    u_xlat2.x = float(1.0) / _ClipWidthCloth;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat48 = clamp(u_xlat48, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat48 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat2.xyz = _ClipColor.xyz + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat48) * u_xlat2.xyz + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;

in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;

float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(_DigiDistore);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);

in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;

{

    u_xlat8.x = min(max(u_xlat8.x, 0.0), 1.0);

    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat20.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat32);

    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;

    u_xlat20.xyz = u_xlat20.xyz * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat20.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat20.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat5.x = (-u_xlat43) * u_xlat43 + 1.0;

    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_39 / u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat16_2.z * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat17;
    u_xlat5.x = min(u_xlat5.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = min(u_xlat16_16.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xyz * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_16.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14 = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_14 = min(max(u_xlat16_14, 0.0), 1.0);
#else

#endif
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = u_xlat20.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_14) + u_xlat16_16.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_14);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_14) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_10.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_14 = min(max(u_xlat16_14, 0.0), 1.0);
#else

#endif
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_14) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = max(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14 = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_2.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat5.x;

    u_xlat16_42 = (-u_xlat5.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;

    u_xlat16_42 = min(max(u_xlat16_42, 0.0), 1.0);
#else

    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);

    u_xlat16_16.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyw = vec3(u_xlat16_38) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_16.xyz;

    u_xlatu0 = uint(int(u_xlat16_16.x));

    u_xlat12 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat43 + 1.0;

    u_xlat16_26 = min(max(u_xlat16_26, 0.0), 1.0);
#else

    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_39);

    u_xlat16_26 = u_xlat12 * u_xlat16_16.x;
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_26) * u_xlat16_10.xyz + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = max(u_xlat16_16.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = min(u_xlat16_16.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_16.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(0.318309873, 0.318309873, 0.318309873) + u_xlat16_16.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyw;
    for(uint u_xlatu_loop_1 = uint(0u) ; u_xlatu_loop_1<u_xlatu0 ; u_xlatu_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat24 = float(int(u_xlatu_loop_1));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb5 = !!(u_xlat24<2.0);
#else

#endif
        u_xlat16_10.xy = (bool(u_xlatb5)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat17 = u_xlat24 + -2.0;
        u_xlat24 = (u_xlatb5) ? u_xlat24 : u_xlat17;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb24 = !!(u_xlat24<1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb24 = u_xlat24<1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_26 = (u_xlatb24) ? u_xlat16_10.x : u_xlat16_10.y;
        u_xlati24 = int(u_xlat16_26);
        u_xlat5.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPosition[u_xlati24].xyz;
        u_xlat41 = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
        u_xlat41 = max(u_xlat41, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat7.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat41);
        u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat7.xxx;
        u_xlat7.x = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat41);
        u_xlat41 = u_xlat41 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati24].x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati24].y;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat41 = min(max(u_xlat41, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat41 = clamp(u_xlat41, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat41 = u_xlat41 * u_xlat7.x;
        u_xlat16_26 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDir[u_xlati24].xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
        u_xlat16_26 = u_xlat16_26 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati24].z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati24].w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_26 = min(max(u_xlat16_26, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_26 = clamp(u_xlat16_26, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_26 = u_xlat16_26 * u_xlat16_26;
        u_xlat41 = u_xlat16_26 * u_xlat41;
        u_xlat16_26 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_26 = min(max(u_xlat16_26, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_26 = clamp(u_xlat16_26, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_26) * _AdditionalLightsColor[u_xlati24].xyz;
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat41) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
        u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_16.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-u_xlat13.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat13.zxy) + (-u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat5.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat5.x);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat5.xxx;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * (-u_xlat13.zxy);
    u_xlat5.xyz = (-u_xlat13.yzx) * u_xlat0.zxy + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat41 = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat41 = inversesqrt(u_xlat41);
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat41) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot((-u_xlat13.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat0.xy * u_xlat16_2.xx;
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_RampMap, u_xlat16_2.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat0.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz / u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb36 = !!(_DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978);
#else
    u_xlatb36 = _DigiBaseColor1.w<0.00999999978;
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (u_xlatb36) ? -1.0 : u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat36 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = vec2(u_xlat36) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat16_36 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat1.xy).x;
    u_xlat16_14 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_14 = min(u_xlat16_14, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_14 * u_xlat16_2.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat16_36 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat36 = (-u_xlat16_2.x) + u_xlat36;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat36 = min(max(u_xlat36, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat36 = clamp(u_xlat36, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = (-_DigiBaseColor0.xyz) * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat36) * u_xlat0.xyz + u_xlat13.xyz;
    u_xlat36 = vs_TEXCOORD2.x + (-_ClipValueCloth);
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / _ClipWidthCloth;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat36 = min(max(u_xlat36, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat36 = clamp(u_xlat36, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat36 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat36;

    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);

    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"

 Pass {
  Name "OUTLINE"
  LOD 300
  Tags { "IGNOREPROJECTOR" = "true" "LIGHTMODE" = "AdvancedOutline" "QUEUE" = "Geometry+200" "RenderType" = "Transparent" }
  GpuProgramID 106830
Program "vp" {
SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "_VCOLOR2N_OFF" "_VTEX_OFF" }
"// hash: 967802496b4ceb9e
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec4 _ScreenParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _OutlineColor;
uniform 	vec4 _lightDir;
uniform 	vec4 _ScreenResolution;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_COLOR0;
varying mediump float vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat6;
float u_xlat9;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = 0.0;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = max(u_xlat9, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(_lightDir.xyz, _lightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * _lightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-_OutlineColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat3.xyz + _OutlineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * in_COLOR0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat1.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_NORMAL0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_NORMAL0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_NORMAL0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xz = u_xlat0.yy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].xy * u_xlat0.xx + u_xlat3.xz;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].xy * u_xlat0.zz + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat6 = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat6 = inversesqrt(u_xlat6);
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat6) * u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy / _ScreenParams.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * _ScreenResolution.yy;
    u_xlat2 = u_xlat1.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat2 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat1.xxxx + u_xlat2;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat1.zzzz + u_xlat2;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * u_xlat1.ww;
    gl_Position.xy = u_xlat0.xy * vec2(0.00462962966, 0.00462962966) + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = 0.00999999978 / u_xlat1.w;
    gl_Position.z = u_xlat0.x + u_xlat1.z;
    gl_Position.w = u_xlat1.w;
    return;
}

#endif

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH
    precision highp float;
#else
    precision mediump float;

uniform 	mediump float _ClipValueCloth;
uniform 	mediump float _ClipWidthCloth;
uniform 	mediump vec3 _ClipColor;

#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_0;

void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD1.w + (-_ClipValueCloth);
    u_xlat16_2.x = float(1.0) / _ClipWidthCloth;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_0.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = _ClipColor.xyz + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * u_xlat16_2.xyz + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;

#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_COLOR0;
out mediump float vs_TEXCOORD0;

{
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = 0.0;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = max(u_xlat9, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(_lightDir.xyz, _lightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * _lightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else

    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;

 Pass {
  Name "ForwardLit"
  LOD 300
  Tags { "IGNOREPROJECTOR" = "true" "LIGHTMODE" = "FurPass1" "QUEUE" = "Geometry+200" "RenderType" = "Transparent" }
  Blend One One, One One
  GpuProgramID 133184
Program "vp" {
SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "_VCOLOR2N_OFF" "_VTEX_OFF" }
"// hash: a28ec0a6c978b4b7
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec4 _Time;
uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	vec4 _DigiST1;
uniform 	mediump float _DigiChange;
uniform 	float _DigiScale;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_COLOR0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump float u_xlat16_1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat12;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = vec2(0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat12 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat12 = max(u_xlat12, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat12 = inversesqrt(u_xlat12);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat12) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1 = min(u_xlat16_1, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1 = (-u_xlat16_1) + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(0.0500000007, 0.0500000007, 0.0500000007);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_1) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * vec3(_DigiScale) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat2.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat2.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat2.zzz + u_xlat2.xyw;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat2.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.w = clamp(u_xlat0.w, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_COLOR0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0.x = in_TEXCOORD0.y * 2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat0.z = (-_DigiChange) * 2.0 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.z = clamp(u_xlat0.z, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyw = in_TEXCOORD0.xyy;
    vs_TEXCOORD2 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat2.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat2.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat2.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 100

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH
    precision highp float;
#else
    precision mediump float;
#endif
precision highp int;
uniform 	mediump float _DigiChange;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _DigiBaseColor0;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _DigiBaseColor1;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _DigiHighColor;
uniform lowp sampler2D _ClothTex;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
float u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
lowp vec2 u_xlat10_3;
bool u_xlatb9;
mediump float u_xlat16_10;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0 = vs_TEXCOORD1.w * vs_TEXCOORD2.w;
    u_xlat16_1.x = _DigiChange;
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2 = (-_DigiBaseColor0) + _DigiBaseColor1;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1.xxxx * u_xlat16_2 + _DigiBaseColor0;
    u_xlat10_3.xy = texture2D(_ClothTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xy;
    u_xlatb9 = u_xlat16_1.w>=u_xlat10_3.x;
    u_xlat16_10 = (u_xlatb9) ? u_xlat0 : 0.0;
    u_xlat16_10 = u_xlat10_3.x * u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat16_2.x = _DigiChange + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_2.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat10_3.y * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * vs_TEXCOORD2.z;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _DigiHighColor.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_10) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"

#define HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS 1
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
#define UNITY_UNIFORM
#else
#define UNITY_UNIFORM uniform
#endif
#define UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION 1
#if UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x) layout(location = x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(binding = x, std140)
#else
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)
#endif
uniform 	vec4 _Time;
uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(1) uniform UnityPerDraw {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LODFade;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightData;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightIndices[2];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_ProbesOcclusion;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_DynamicLightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHC;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _OutlineColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _OutlineWidth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Offset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _lightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _ScreenResolution;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _DigiST1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DigiChange;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiBaseColor0;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiBaseColor1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiHighColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DigiScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_COLOR0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat4;
bool u_xlatb4;
float u_xlat8;
float u_xlat12;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).y;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.z = 0.0;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat0.x * in_TEXCOORD0.y + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xy = min(u_xlat16_1.xx, vec2(1.0, 0.0));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb4 = !!(u_xlat4>=u_xlat16_1.y);
#else
    u_xlatb4 = u_xlat4>=u_xlat16_1.y;
#endif
    u_xlat4 = u_xlatb4 ? 1.0 : float(0.0);
    u_xlat8 = (-u_xlat4) * u_xlat0.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat4;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_1.y * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-u_xlat16_1.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.xyw = u_xlat0.xxx * in_NORMAL0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.w = u_xlat8;
    u_xlat2.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(0.0500000007, 0.0500000007, 0.0500000007);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * vec3(_DigiScale) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyw * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat12 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat12 = max(u_xlat12, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat12 = inversesqrt(u_xlat12);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat12) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.w = min(max(u_xlat1.w, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.w = clamp(u_xlat1.w, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_COLOR0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat12 = in_TEXCOORD0.y * 2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat1.z = (-_DigiChange) * 2.0 + u_xlat12;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.z = min(max(u_xlat1.z, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.z = clamp(u_xlat1.z, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xyw = in_TEXCOORD0.xyy;
    vs_TEXCOORD2 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#endif

    u_xlat0 = vs_TEXCOORD1.w * vs_TEXCOORD2.w;
    u_xlat16_1.x = _DigiChange;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2 = (-_DigiBaseColor0) + _DigiBaseColor1;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1.xxxx * u_xlat16_2 + _DigiBaseColor0;
    u_xlat16_3.xy = texture(_ClothTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xy;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb9 = !!(u_xlat16_1.w>=u_xlat16_3.x);
#else
    u_xlatb9 = u_xlat16_1.w>=u_xlat16_3.x;
#endif
    u_xlat16_10 = (u_xlatb9) ? u_xlat0 : 0.0;
    u_xlat16_10 = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat16_2.x = _DigiChange + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_2.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * vs_TEXCOORD2.z;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _DigiHighColor.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_10) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

uniform 	mediump float _DigiChange;
uniform 	float _DigiScale;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_COLOR0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump float u_xlat16_1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat12;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = u_xlat0.xy;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = vec2(0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat12 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat12 = max(u_xlat12, 1.17549435e-38);

    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat12) * u_xlat0.xyz;

    u_xlat16_1 = min(u_xlat16_1, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1 = (-u_xlat16_1) + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(0.0500000007, 0.0500000007, 0.0500000007);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_1) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * vec3(_DigiScale) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat2.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat2.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat2.zzz + u_xlat2.xyw;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat2.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.w = clamp(u_xlat0.w, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_COLOR0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0.x = in_TEXCOORD0.y * 2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat0.z = (-_DigiChange) * 2.0 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.z = clamp(u_xlat0.z, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyw = in_TEXCOORD0.xyy;
    vs_TEXCOORD2 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat2.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat2.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat2.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;

mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
lowp vec2 u_xlat10_3;

    u_xlat16_1.x = _DigiChange;
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2 = (-_DigiBaseColor0) + _DigiBaseColor1;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1.xxxx * u_xlat16_2 + _DigiBaseColor0;
    u_xlat10_3.xy = texture2D(_ClothTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xy;
    u_xlatb9 = u_xlat16_1.w>=u_xlat10_3.x;
    u_xlat16_10 = (u_xlatb9) ? u_xlat0 : 0.0;
    u_xlat16_10 = u_xlat10_3.x * u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat16_2.x = _DigiChange + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_2.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat10_3.y * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * vs_TEXCOORD2.z;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _DigiHighColor.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_10) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;

    u_xlat2.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(0.0500000007, 0.0500000007, 0.0500000007);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * vec3(_DigiScale) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyw * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat12 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat12 = max(u_xlat12, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat12 = inversesqrt(u_xlat12);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat12) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.w = min(max(u_xlat1.w, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.w = clamp(u_xlat1.w, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_COLOR0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat12 = in_TEXCOORD0.y * 2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat1.z = (-_DigiChange) * 2.0 + u_xlat12;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.z = min(max(u_xlat1.z, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.z = clamp(u_xlat1.z, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xyw = in_TEXCOORD0.xyy;
    vs_TEXCOORD2 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 300 es

precision highp float;
precision highp int;
#define HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS 1
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
#define UNITY_UNIFORM
#else
#define UNITY_UNIFORM uniform
#endif
#define UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION 1
#if UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x) layout(location = x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(binding = x, std140)
#else
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)
#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _OutlineColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _OutlineWidth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Offset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _lightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _ScreenResolution;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _DigiST1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DigiChange;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiBaseColor0;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiBaseColor1;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _DigiHighColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM float _DigiScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD2;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
float u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_3;
bool u_xlatb9;
mediump float u_xlat16_10;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0 = vs_TEXCOORD1.w * vs_TEXCOORD2.w;
    u_xlat16_1.x = _DigiChange;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2 = (-_DigiBaseColor0) + _DigiBaseColor1;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1.xxxx * u_xlat16_2 + _DigiBaseColor0;
    u_xlat16_3.xy = texture(_ClothTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xy;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb9 = !!(u_xlat16_1.w>=u_xlat16_3.x);
#else
    u_xlatb9 = u_xlat16_1.w>=u_xlat16_3.x;
#endif
    u_xlat16_10 = (u_xlatb9) ? u_xlat0 : 0.0;
    u_xlat16_10 = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_10;
    u_xlat16_2.x = _DigiChange + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat16_2.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * vs_TEXCOORD2.z;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _DigiHighColor.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_10) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}
}
